FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777539988
OL,3,CGraves identified of two missing
OL,4,Csoldiers more than a century later
OL,6,FResearchers identified the final
OL,7,Fresting place of the two men and
OL,8,Frededication services have taken place.
OL,10,FWilliam Voice joined the Army in 2016.
OL,11,FHis service record has not survived
OL,12,Fbut we know that he was awarded the
OL,13,FMilitary Medal.
OL,15,FHe was killed or went missing in the
OL,16,Farea of Klein Zillebeke, on 1st August
OL,17,F1917, during repeated shelling, and
OL,18,Fhis remains could not be identified.
OL,19,FHis name was placed on the Menin Gate
OL,20,FMemorial to the missing in Ypres.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
