OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777539988
OL,3,CGraves identified of two missing
OL,4,Csoldiers more than a century later
OL,6,FOn the morning of the 29 September
OL,7,F1918 the 10th Battalion formed up to
OL,8,Fattack along the eastern side of the
OL,9,FYpres-Comines canal. The war diary
OL,10,Frecords that this was their first
OL,11,Fexperience of open warfare that year.
OL,13,FThe total casualties by the end of the
OL,14,Fday were substantial, and Lionel was
OL,15,Fone of those killed. Records of his
OL,16,Fdeath were lost, and after the war his
OL,17,Fname was placed on the Menin Gate
OL,18,FMemorial to the Missing at Ypres.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777539988
OL,3,CGraves identified of two missing
OL,4,Csoldiers more than a century later
OL,6,FBut research has now revealed that
OL,7,FLionel was in fact buried at
OL,8,FZantvoorde.
OL,10,FRededication services for both men
OL,11,Fwere organised by the MOD's Joint
OL,12,FCasualty and Compassionate Centre
OL,13,F(JCCC), also known as the 'War
OL,14,FDetectives'.
OL,16,FThe service for LCpl Voice was held at
OL,17,Fthe Commonwealth War Graves
OL,18,FCommission's Bedford House Cemetery
OL,19,Fand the service for LCpl Sandell took
OL,20,Fplace at Zantvoorde British Cemetery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777539988
OL,3,CGraves identified of two missing
OL,4,Csoldiers more than a century later
OL,6,FFergus Read, Commemorations Case
OL,7,FOfficer at CWGC, said: "We are
OL,8,Fprivileged to support the
OL,9,Frededications of Lance Corporal Voice
OL,10,Fand Lance Corporal Sandell's graves.
OL,11,FThanks to the efforts of many, we are
OL,12,Fhonoured to mark their final resting
OL,13,Fplaces with new headstones bearing
OL,14,Ftheir names and personal inscriptions
OL,15,Fchosen by their family, on behalf of
OL,16,Fthose who loved them a century ago.
OL,26,@oD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
